        12
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northville%2C_Fulton_County%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "In 1824 a post office opened, and by 1827 the settlement officially adopted the name Northville.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        13
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Northville%2C_Fulton_County%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The 1873 incorporation coincided with a lumber boom that spawned mills, cooperage, tanning, and woodenware factories.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
